No. —, Original.

Ex parte: In the matter of Kingston Dry Dock Construction Company, Inc., petitioner. Submitted October 6, 1924. Decided October 13, 1924. Mr. D. M. Tibbets and Mr. John M. Woolsey for petitioner.

Motion for leave to file petition for a writ of prohibition and/or a writ of mandamus herein denied.
